SWEDISH SIMPLICITY

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="200" height_tablet="100" height_mobile="70"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row_content" tlg_padding="pt0 pb0" css=".vc_custom_1569827621347{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;background-color: #f2f2ed !important;}"][vc_column offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][tlg_spacer height="90" height_tablet="90" height_mobile="90"][vc_column_text]

THE SWEDISH TECH CHALLENGER

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="32" height_tablet="32" height_mobile="32"][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1569242578994{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}"][vc_column_inner css=".vc_custom_1569242276199{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1569242794183{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}"]

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="32" height_tablet="32" height_mobile="32"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]

Swedes like to keep things simple. We like it when the products we use are intuitive and work for us, helping us improve our lives. Not the other way around.

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="32" height_tablet="32" height_mobile="32"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_column_text]

Sweden is at the forefront of digitalization. We are constantly developing and embracing new technology. But for Swedes, balance is everything, so we always make sure that just as much Heart as Brain go into the mix. We do this for good reasons.

Digitalization has the power to become the greatest tool for democracy ever developed. But, as we have already seen, the same technology can be used against us.
Governments around the world. Tech Giants in Silicon Valley. Mobile Phone companies.

We all have a responsibility in making sure that the digital citizens in a connected world are safe. Safe from inappropriate usage. Data mining. Radiation.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_column_text]

So why would a Mobile Phone Company such as Dahl Mobile talk of the threats of technology?
Well, Swedes are honest and we still believe that the benefits of a connected world exceeds the dangers, if we dare to address them. We are ready to take our responsibility, and urge others to do so as well.

The benefits of Swedish digitalization needs to benefit all. We have a strong feeling of that what’s right is right and that if you make money, you should give money back. That’s why 10 % of all our profits are re-invested in the local market. It’s also the reason why we’re committed to supporting the opening of both a Tech Campus and an assembly facility in South Africa.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_column_text]

On a larger scale, we do everything in our power to make sure that we as a company and our products are as eco-friendly and sustainable as possible. Our components are carefully selected with sustainability in mind and we build our devices to have a greater lifespan than the competition.

We are Dahl Mobile and we are from Sweden. We believe that everyone should have access to affordable mobile technology - intuitive products that help improve lives and connect the world in order to improve it.

We call that Swedish Simplicity.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][tlg_spacer height="60" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="60"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1569243520493{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}"]

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="60" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="60"][vc_column_text]

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570119935730{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]It only took a few decades for digitalization to change almost everything; The way we consume media, hang out with our peers, perform our financial matters and our shopping. A CONNECTED WORLD AT DIFFERENT LEVELS

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570119962841{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]The world in general is not an equal place. item.title: Privacy Policy
item.dc:creator: Fredrik
item.content:encoded:
Who we are

Our website address is: http://dahlmobile.com.

What personal data we collect and why we collect it

Comments

When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor’s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.

An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.

Media

If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.

Contact forms

Cookies

If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.

If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.

When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select "Remember Me", your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.

If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.

Embedded content from other websites

Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.

These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.

Analytics

Who we share your data with

How long we retain your data

If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.

For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.

What rights you have over your data

If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.

Where we send your data

Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.

Your contact information

Additional information

How we protect your data

What data breach procedures we have in place

What third parties we receive data from

What automated decision making and/or profiling we do with user data

Industry regulatory disclosure requirements

DAHL PEOPLE +

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570126254832{margin-top: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]
ENABLING DIGITAL CITIZENSHIPS
[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="32" height_tablet="32" height_mobile="32"][vc_column_text]The ‘new world’ is a Modern world where everyone likes to be ‘in the know’ and ‘stay-up-to-date’. It is a world where people are constantly interested in new things and have a desire to learn more. For these citizens Technology does not stress them out – it empowers them to discover new experiences. They are optimistic about the future and spend a lot of time online – socializing, surfing, streaming, gaming. The right to participate in the digital world is a human right. With the Dahl People + range of devices, we have ensured that cutting edge, intuitive mobile technology has been applied to bring to as many people as possible, a product of the highest quality, reliability and functionality, while at the same time remaining affordable. We are passionate about what we do and our focus is to ensure that we bring a human and sustainable digitalization to the market, where our products and services are designed and developed with the intention to increase quality of life. We dream of a world where we are able to make the difference. Welcome to our World. Launch in Q1 2020[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="1" height_tablet="32" height_mobile="32"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_hidden-xs"][vc_single_image image="545" img_size="full" alignment="center"][/vc_column][vc_column el_class="stick-to-top"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" tlg_padding="pt0 pb0" tlg_parallax="not-parallax" tlg_equal_height="equal-height"][vc_column width="1/4" css=".vc_custom_1570123536805{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;border-right-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;border-right-color: #e5eaed !important;border-right-style: solid !important;}" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][mvc_ihe border_width="0" hover_effect="square effect7" image_id="273" caption_url="|title:Product%20range||" caption_bg="rgba(0,0,0,0.01)"][/mvc_ihe][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570126449368{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]

FUNCTIONALITY

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1571749545385{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]DUAL SIM Fitted with Dual SIM, enabling separate call and data SIMS or separate call numbers. With a dedicated data SIM, you become the saviour in your group, through Hotspot Sharing your access to the Internet. SD CARD With the added benefit of an SD Card Slot, allowing storage for thousands of your favourite tunes, videos and images. BUILT IN GPS The Global Positioning System (GPS) is a space based navigation system that makes sure you will never be lost again.[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="60" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="60"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4" css=".vc_custom_1570123527687{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;border-right-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;border-right-color: #e5eaed !important;border-right-style: solid !important;}" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][mvc_ihe border_width="0" hover_effect="square effect7" image_id="274" caption_url="|title:Product%20range||" caption_bg="rgba(0,0,0,0.01)"][/mvc_ihe][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570126458039{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="32" height_tablet="32" height_mobile="32"][vc_column_text]The Dahl Intro range of phones have been designed with simplicity and functionality in mind. Available in 3 model ranges and several different colour options the Dahl Intro will always keep you connected and in the mood. Dahl InTro+, Dahl InTro Dahl InTro Lite With the Dahl Intro range of devices, we have ensured that technology has been applied to bring a product of the highest reliability and functionality, while at the same time still remaining affordable. We are passionate about what we do and our focus is to ensure that we bring a human and sustainable digitalization to the market, where our products and services are designed and developed with the intention to increase quality of life. InTouch III

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570122496315{margin-top: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]

CRAFTSMANSHIP IN EVERY DETAIL

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="32" height_tablet="32" height_mobile="32"][vc_column_text]The new InTouch III  lets you experience digitalization at the highest level. Our Pro range has been carefully crafted to support the individual that demands the highest quality, reliability and technological innovation from their device whether it be for work or play. With its large curved Amoled screen and powerful processing capabilities, it has never
been more fun to revisit those memories, do your work, play games or stream videos.

With the InTouch III range of devices, we have ensured that cutting edge, intuitive mobile technology has been applied to bring a product of the highest quality, reliability and functionality, while at the same time still remaining affordable.

We are passionate about what we do and our focus is to ensure that we bring a human and sustainable digitalization to the market, where our products and services are designed and developed with the intention to increase quality of life.

Welcome to our World.[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="1" height_tablet="32" height_mobile="32"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_hidden-xs"][vc_single_image image="1372" img_size="full" alignment="center" onclick="zoom" css_animation="rotateIn"][/vc_column][vc_column el_class="stick-to-top"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" tlg_padding="pt0 pb0" tlg_parallax="not-parallax" tlg_equal_height="equal-height"][vc_column width="1/4" css=".vc_custom_1570123536805{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;border-right-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;border-right-color: #e5eaed !important;border-right-style: solid !important;}" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][mvc_ihe border_width="0" hover_effect="square effect7" image_id="1346" caption_url="|title:Product%20range||" caption_bg="rgba(0,0,0,0.01)" alt="525*525"][/mvc_ihe][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570123899282{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]

YOUR PHONE. YOUR WAY.

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1685173814624{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]SECURITY
InTouch  users have the choice of how they want to securely access their device. Access Pin, Use Face-ID, Shape code or Fingerprint protection. It’s your choice!

WORK HARD, PLAY HARD
Whether you intend to work hard or play hard, Dahl Pro has what it takes. With its powerful core processor and large internal memory, you will experience outstanding performance that will meet all your expectations.

LONG ENDURANCE, QUICK RECOVERY
The Pro’s power management optimises allocation intelligently, ensuring a smoother performance. Fast charge 20 minute recovery mode fully restores your device.[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="60" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="60"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4" css=".vc_custom_1570123527687{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;border-right-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;border-right-color: #e5eaed !important;border-right-style: solid !important;}" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][mvc_ihe border_width="0" hover_effect="square effect7" image_id="1347" caption_url="|title:Product%20range||" caption_bg="rgba(0,0,0,0.01)"][/mvc_ihe][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570124893324{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]

GAME CHANGING DISPLAY

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1685173886261{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]CRYSTAL CLEAR SCREEN
InTouch  is equipped with an advanced curved Amoled Screen. Compared to traditional screens, it offers a wider vision, a higher refresh rate to smoothen your experience. It delivers rich colours, vivid images and a stunning immersive effect. Images and videos are much clearer and more colourful, with the smartphone being thinner and lighter at the same time.

GORILLA GLASS
The display features the Corning Gorilla Glass 5: a glass solution that really raises the bar for protection.[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="60" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="60"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4" css=".vc_custom_1570123518197{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;border-right-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;border-right-color: #e5eaed !important;border-right-style: solid !important;}" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][mvc_ihe border_width="0" hover_effect="square effect7" image_id="1350" caption_url="|title:Product%20range||" caption_bg="rgba(0,0,0,0.01)" alt="325*325"][/mvc_ihe][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570124676279{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]

These devices while innovative in design will be of the highest quality, reliability and functionality and at the same time remain affordable. We are passionate about what we do and while we are pioneering and introducing new technology our focus will always remain that we bring a human and sustainable digitalization to the market, where our products and services are designed and developed with the intention to increase quality of life. MISSION, GOALS & VISION

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="350" height_tablet="350" height_mobile="350"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" tlg_padding="pt0 pb0" tlg_enable_overlay="yes" tlg_bg_overlay="rgba(255,255,255,0.01)"][vc_column parallax="content-moving" parallax_image="616" offset="vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1586186075435{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;}"]

MISSION, GOALS & VISION

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column css_animation="bounceInLeft" width="1/2"][vc_column_text]

MISSION

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Dahl Sweden Mobile Technology AB is a Swedish manufacture of Smartphones, tablets, laptops, accessories and developer of applications. We are selling to the international market through e-commerce, collaboration agreements with operators, agents, distributors and retailers. We are driven by new thinking. Our ambition is to become one of the top ten smart phone companies in the world in terms of quality and technology.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="bounceInRight" width="1/2"][vc_column_text]

GOALS & VISION

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]In the next two years we hope to become an established brand in the international smartphone market. Our 5 year goal is to obtain at least 3 percent of the smartphone market. Once achieved this will give us annual sales of 50 to 60 million units with a sales value of  45 to 90 billion Swedish kronor ($ 6 – 20 billions USD), based on anticipated model mix.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column offset="vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md"][vc_single_image image="646" img_size="" alignment="center" css_animation="fadeIn"][/vc_column][/vc_row]

CORPORATE GOVERNANCE

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="350" height_tablet="350" height_mobile="350"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" tlg_padding="pt0 pb0" tlg_enable_overlay="yes" tlg_bg_overlay="rgba(255,255,255,0.01)"][vc_column parallax="content-moving" parallax_image="620" offset="vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1586184638300{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;}"]

CORPORATE GOVERNANCE

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column css_animation="bounceInLeft"][vc_column_text]

CORPORATE GOVERNANCE

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Dahl Sweden Mobile Technology AB is a Swedish public limited company with head offices registered in Sweden. The company was registered with the Swedish Companies Registration Office on 5 June 2011. The Company complies with the Swedish Companies Act (2005: 551) and other applicable laws and regulations in Sweden.. The basis for the Company's operations is the articles of association. The business of the company is to develop, manufacture, import, export and trade in mobile phones, personal computers and accessories as stated in §3 of the Articles of Association. The AGM adopts the articles of association and annually appoints the Board of Directors. The Board of Directors is responsible for the Company's organization and administration and appoints or dismisses the CEO. Each year, the Board of Directors adopts a written rules of procedure for its work, combined with a CEO's instructions for allocating the work between the Board and the CEO. Questions relating to remuneration or auditing are decided directly by the Company's Board of Directors. All members of the Board are elected until the next Annual General Meeting. Every individual member of the Board of Directors has the right to resign at any time[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column offset="vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md"][vc_single_image image="646" img_size="" alignment="center" css_animation="fadeIn"][/vc_column][/vc_row]

DAHL PEOPLE (4G)

VERY SPECIAL OFFER! ONLY 49 USD.

Note: Purchase only available at Dahl Mobile e-commerce.

 [/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570126254832{margin-top: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]

ENABLING DIGITAL CITIZENSHIPS

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="32" height_tablet="32" height_mobile="32"][vc_column_text]The ‘new world’ is a Modern world where everyone likes to be ‘in the know’ and ‘stay-up-to-date’. It is a world where people are constantly interested in new things and have a desire to learn more. For these citizens Technology does not stress them out – it empowers them to discover new experiences. They are optimistic about the future and spend a lot of time online – socializing, surfing, streaming, gaming.

The right to participate in the digital world is a human right.
With the Dahl People 4G range of devices, we have ensured that cutting edge, intuitive mobile technology has been applied to bring to as many people as possible, a product of the highest quality, reliability and functionality, while at the same time remaining affordable.

We are passionate about what we do and our focus is to ensure that we bring a human and sustainable digitalization to the market, where our products and services are designed and developed with the intention to increase quality of life. We dream of a world where we are able to make the difference.

Welcome to our World.

Launch in Q3 2024[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="1" height_tablet="32" height_mobile="32"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_hidden-xs"][vc_single_image image="1672" img_size="full" alignment="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" tlg_padding="pt0 pb0" tlg_parallax="not-parallax" tlg_equal_height="equal-height"][vc_column width="1/4" css=".vc_custom_1570123536805{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;border-right-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;border-right-color: #e5eaed !important;border-right-style: solid !important;}" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][mvc_ihe border_width="0" hover_effect="square effect7" image_id="1673" caption_url="|title:Product%20range||" caption_bg="rgba(0,0,0,0.01)"][/mvc_ihe][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570126449368{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]

FUNCTIONALITY

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1571749545385{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]DUAL SIM
Fitted with Dual SIM, enabling separate call and data SIMS or separate call numbers. With a dedicated data SIM, you become the saviour in your group, through Hotspot Sharing your access to the Internet.

SD CARD
With the added benefit of an SD Card Slot, allowing storage for thousands of your favourite tunes, videos and images.

BUILT IN GPS
The Global Positioning System (GPS) is a space based navigation system that makes sure you will never be lost again.[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="60" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="60"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4" css=".vc_custom_1570123527687{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;border-right-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;border-right-color: #e5eaed !important;border-right-style: solid !important;}" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][mvc_ihe border_width="0" hover_effect="square effect7" image_id="1675" caption_url="|title:Product%20range||" caption_bg="rgba(0,0,0,0.01)"][/mvc_ihe][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570126458039{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]

INNOVATION

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1722530913600{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]CAMERA

MAIN CAMERA Triple 48 MP, f/1.8, (wide), 1/2.0", 0.8µm, PDAF
2 MP, f/2.4, (macro)
2 MP, f/2.4, (depth)
SELFIE CAMERA Single 8 MP, f/2.0, (wide)
Features HDR

The main camera with triple LED and Touch Focus Picture in High Dynamic Range lets you take great pictures. The front facing 5MP camera has a flash, so you are ready to make video calls, even in the dark.

SECURITY ACCESS
Dahl People 5G users have the choice of how they want to securely access their device. Access Pin, Shape code or Fingerprint protection. It’s your choice.

LIGHT
Packed with technical and innovative features, the phone remains light, weighing in at only

Weight 193 g (6.81 oz)

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="60" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="60"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4" css=".vc_custom_1570123518197{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;border-right-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;border-right-color: #e5eaed !important;border-right-style: solid !important;}" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][mvc_ihe border_width="0" hover_effect="square effect7" image_id="1673" caption_url="|title:Product%20range||" caption_bg="rgba(0,0,0,0.01)"][/mvc_ihe][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570126467325{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]

PERFORMANCE

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1722530652245{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]5G PHONE
When you buy a Dahl People 5G, you are equipping yourself with the latest in Swedish innovation, quality and design.

STAYING POWER
Dahl People 5G is fitted with a 5000 mAh battery to ensure that you have the staying power to meet the demands of your daily usage.

SCREEN

DISPLAY Type IPS LCD
Size 6.58 inches, 104.3 cm2 (~84.5% screen-to-body ratio)
Resolution 1080 x 2408 pixels, 20:9 ratio (~401 ppi density)

Enjoy your photos, favorite movies and games with great, crisp picture quality.[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="60" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="60"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4" css=".vc_custom_1570123505059{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][mvc_ihe border_width="0" hover_effect="square effect7" image_id="1680" caption_url="|title:Product%20range||" caption_bg="rgba(0,0,0,0.01)"][/mvc_ihe][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570125029593{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]

RELIABILITY

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1722568103214{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]PEACE OF MIND
All Dahl Mobile products meet the strictest testing prior to market introduction. All our products have been globally, as well as locally certified.

COMPONENTS
Each and every phone is built using the best quality components available.

KEYTAG

Dahl Mobile has developed a key tag which can be attached to your key or bag and can find them in case you lose them.

CUSTOMER CARE
At Dahl Mobile, we take customer care seriously. All our phones can be repaired at local repair centres. The warranty conditions that apply for your market, are clearly documented with the purchase of your smartphone.[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="60" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="60"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" tlg_padding="pt0 pb0" tlg_parallax="not-parallax" tlg_equal_height="equal-height"][vc_column width="1/4" css=".vc_custom_1570126718204{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;border-right-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;border-right-color: #e5eaed !important;border-right-style: solid !important;}" offset="vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md"][mvc_ihe border_width="0" hover_effect="square effect7" image_id="273" caption_url="|title:Product%20range||" caption_bg="rgba(0,0,0,0.01)"][/mvc_ihe][tlg_spacer height="0" height_tablet="20" height_mobile="20"][vc_column_text]

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]DUAL SIM

SD CARD

BUILT IN GPS

INNOVATION

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]CAMERA
The main 13MP camera with dual tone LED and Touch Focus Picture in High Dynamic Range lets you take great pictures. The front facing 5MP camera has a flash, so you are ready to make video calls, even in the dark.

SECURITY ACCESS

ARTICLES OF ASSOCIATION

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Articles of Association for Dahl Sweden Mobile Technology AB (publ) Adopted 2016-11-22 §1 Company name The company name is Dahl Sweden Mobile Technology AB (publ). §2 Recidence The Board of Directors shall have its registered office in Stockholm (county), Solna (municipality). §3 Business The business of the company is to conduct development, manufacture, import, export and trade in mobile phones, personal computers and accessories for these and related activities. §4 Share capital The share capital shall be at least SEK 500,000 and not more than SEK 2,000,000. §5 Number of shares The company shall have a minimum of 50,000,000 and a maximum of 200,000,000 shares. §6 Board of Directors The Board of Directors shall consist of at least three members and a maximum of ten members with a minimum of zero and a maximum of ten deputies. The Board of Directors is elected annually at the Annual General Meeting for the period until the next Annual General Meeting has been held. §7 Auditor An auditor with or without deputy auditor is appointed for examination of the company's annual report and the administration of the Board and the CEO. §8 Notice of Annual General Meeting Notice of a general meeting shall be made by letter by post, no earlier than six and no later than two weeks before the meeting. §9 Issues at the Annual General Meeting At the Annual General Meeting, the following matters shall occur. 1. Election of Chairman of the Meeting. 2. Preparation and approval of voting list. 3. Where applicable, the election of one or more secretary. 4. Examination of whether the meeting has been duly convened. 5. Approval of the draft agenda. 6. Presentation of the annual report and audit report. 7. Decision regarding a. Establishment of the income statement and balance sheet, b. Disposals of the company's profit or loss according to the established balance sheet; and c. Discharge from the board of directors and the CEO. 8. Determination of fees for the board and auditor. 9. Election of the Board of Directors and the auditor, and, if applicable, deputy members of the Board of Directors and deputy auditors. 10. Other matter, which arrives at the General Meeting according to the Swedish Companies Act or the Articles of Association. §10 Reconciliation reservations The shareholder or trustee are included in the share register on the record date and recorded in a record register pursuant to Chapter 4. the Act (1998: 1479) on the account management of financial are instruments or the one that is recorded on the reconciliation account in accordance with Chapter 4. Section 18, first paragraph, 6-8, shall be presumed to have the authority to exercise the rights set out in Chapter 4. Section 39 of the Swedish Companies Act (2005: 551) §11 Financial year The company's financial year shall cover the period from 1 January to 31 December.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column offset="vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md"][vc_single_image image="646" img_size="" alignment="center" css_animation="fadeIn"][/vc_column][/vc_row]

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="350" height_tablet="350" height_mobile="350"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" tlg_padding="pt0 pb0" tlg_enable_overlay="yes" tlg_bg_overlay="rgba(255,255,255,0.01)"][vc_column parallax="content-moving" parallax_image="626" offset="vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1586184738196{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;}"]

ANNUAL GENERAL MEETING

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column css_animation="bounceInLeft"][vc_column_text]

ANNUAL GENERAL MEETING

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Ultimately, it is the shareholders who determinate the way Dahl Sweden Mobile Technology AB (publ) is governed. Shareholders exercise their rights at general meetings of shareholders. The General Meeting of Shareholders is the governing body. The annual General Meeting (AGM) addresses changes in the principal governing document, the Articles of Association. The AGM approves the financial results and balance sheet, discharges the Board from liability, elects a new Board, elects auditors and resolves on the remuneration of the Chairman of the Board, the Board members and the auditors and resolves on guidelines for the remuneration of senior executives and on changes in the number of shares and the share structure. The official notification of the AGM is dispatched no earlier than six and no later than four (two) weeks prior to the Meeting. The notification is to include information on the manner of and the final date for notification of attendance, the right to participate and vote at the Meeting, a numbered agenda showing the matters to be addressed, information on the appropriation of earnings, and the main content of other proposals.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Shareholders or their representatives may vote for the full number of shares owned or represented. One share carries one vote at the general meeting of shareholders. Intention to attend the AGM is primarily notified by e-mail, in accordance with the instructions in the official notification. For participation as a representative, the shareholder must issue a power of attorney to the representative. If the shares are registered with a nominee, they must be re-registered in the shareholder´s name in the share register no later than the record date of the Meeting. The record date is stated in the notification of the meeting. Official notification of an Extraordinary General Meeting (EGM), at which the matter of the company´s Articles of Association is to be dealt with, must be issued no earlier than six weeks and no later than four (two) weeks prior to the Meeting. Notification of any other EGM must be issued no earlier than six weeks and no later than three weeks of the Meeting.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column offset="vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md"][vc_single_image image="646" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="fadeIn"][/vc_column][/vc_row]

 [/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570126254832{margin-top: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]

ENABLING DIGITAL CITIZENSHIPS

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="32" height_tablet="32" height_mobile="32"][vc_column_text]The ‘new world’ is a Modern world where everyone likes to be ‘in the know’ and ‘stay-up-to-date’. It is a world where people are constantly interested in new things and have a desire to learn more. For these citizens Technology does not stress them out – it empowers them to discover new experiences. They are optimistic about the future and spend a lot of time online – socializing, surfing, streaming, gaming.

The right to participate in the digital world is a human right.
With the Dahl phone range of devices, we have ensured that cutting edge, intuitive mobile technology has been applied to bring to as many people as possible, a product of the highest quality, reliability and functionality, while at the same time remaining affordable.

InTouch I. 5G

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570126254832{margin-top: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]

ENABLING DIGITAL CITIZENSHIPS

[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="32" height_tablet="32" height_mobile="32"][vc_column_text]The ‘new world’ is a Modern world where everyone likes to be ‘in the know’ and ‘stay-up-to-date’. It is a world where people are constantly interested in new things and have a desire to learn more. For these citizens Technology does not stress them out – it empowers them to discover new experiences. They are optimistic about the future and spend a lot of time online – socializing, surfing, streaming, gaming.

The right to participate in the digital world is a human right.
With the Dahl phone range of devices, we have ensured that cutting edge, intuitive mobile technology has been applied to bring to as many people as possible, a product of the highest quality, reliability and functionality, while at the same time remaining affordable.

We are passionate about what we do and our focus is to ensure that we bring a human and sustainable digitalization to the market, where our products and services are designed and developed with the intention to increase quality of life. We dream of a world where we are able to make the difference.

Welcome to our World.

Launch in Q2 2023[/vc_column_text][tlg_spacer height="1" height_tablet="32" height_mobile="32"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_hidden-xs"][vc_single_image image="1431" img_size="600*600" onclick="zoom" css_animation="rotateInDownLeft"][vc_single_image image="1435" img_size="600*600" onclick="zoom" css_animation="rotateIn"][/vc_column][vc_column el_class="stick-to-top"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" tlg_padding="pt0 pb0" tlg_parallax="not-parallax" tlg_equal_height="equal-height"][vc_column width="1/4" css=".vc_custom_1570123536805{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;border-right-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;border-right-color: #e5eaed !important;border-right-style: solid !important;}" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][mvc_ihe border_width="0" hover_effect="square effect7" image_id="1301" caption_url="|title:Product%20range||" caption_bg="rgba(0,0,0,0.01)" width="425" height="425"][/mvc_ihe][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1570126449368{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 25px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]

Fitted with Dual SIM, enabling separate call and data SIMS or separate call numbers. With a dedicated data SIM, you become the saviour in your group, through Hotspot Sharing your access to the Internet.

SD CARD
With the added benefit of an SD Card Slot, allowing storage for thousands of your favourite tunes, videos and images.

BUILT IN GPS

The main 48MP camera with dual tone LED and Touch Focus Picture in High Dynamic Range lets you take great pictures. The front facing 5MP camera has a flash, so you are ready to make video calls, even in the dark.

SECURITY ACCESS
Dahlphone  users have the choice of how they want to securely access their device. Access Pin, Shape code or Fingerprint protection. It’s your choice.

STAYING POWER
Dahl People + is fitted with a 5150 mAh battery to ensure that you have the staying power to meet the demands of your daily usage.

The Dahl People + boasts a 1650 x 720 resolution HD (High Definition) IPS LCD, 6.7 inch screen. All Dahl Mobile products meet the strictest testing prior to market introduction. All our products have been globally, as well as locally certified.

COMPONENTS
Each and every phone is built using the best quality components available.

CUSTOMER CARE
At Dahl Mobile, we take customer care seriously. All our phones can be repaired at local repair centres. For these citizens Technology does not stress them out – it empowers them to discover new experiences. They are optimistic about the future and spend a lot of time online – socializing, surfing, streaming, gaming.

The right to participate in the digital world is a human right.
With the Dahl People 4G) range of devices, we have ensured that cutting edge, intuitive mobile technology has been applied to bring to as many people as possible, a product of the highest quality, reliability and functionality, while at the same time remaining affordable.

We are passionate about what we do and our focus is to ensure that we bring a human and sustainable digitalization to the market, where our products and services are designed and developed with the intention to increase quality of life. We dream of a world where we are able to make the difference.

Welcome to our World.
